{"abstract": "The first lesson is never trust a central banker when he or she makes a commitment or gives guidance, writes Swaha Pattanaik of Reuters Breakingviews.", "web_url": "https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2015/01/15/the-swiss-give-a-scary-lesson-on-the-limits-of-central-banks/", "snippet": "The first lesson is never trust a central banker when he or she makes a commitment or gives guidance, writes Swaha Pattanaik of Reuters Breakingviews.", "lead_paragraph": "Central bankers have to live up to high expectations. Investors and politicians expect them to control inflation, prevent deflation, promote growth and keep the financial system healthy. The Swiss National Bank, an above-average institution, has failed at two simpler tasks, keeping its word and preventing destabilizing currency moves. The lessons for the rest of the world are scary.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/01/16/business/dbpix-swissfranc1/dbpix-swissfranc1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 400, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2015/01/16/business/dbpix-swissfranc1/dbpix-swissfranc1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 400}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/01/16/business/dbpix-swissfranc1/dbpix-swissfranc1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 683, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/01/16/business/dbpix-swissfranc1/dbpix-swissfranc1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1365, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2015/01/16/business/dbpix-swissfranc1/dbpix-swissfranc1-thumbStandard.jpg